Renren,is,a,Chinese,social,network,to,find,old,friends,and,meet,new,ones,The,Renren,API,is,an,open,platform,based,on,Open,Social,After,authenticating,developers,can,retrieve,friend,lists,and,check,friend,status,between,users,The,API,also,has,access,to,notifications,and,invitations,Two,of,the,more,unique,services,provided,by,the,API,lets,users,pay,for,certain,applications,and,allows,developers,to,register,new,users